h(x) = \frac{\int \limits_{-\infty}^{\infty}f(t)g(t+x)\mathrm dt}{\sqrt{\int \limits_{-\infty}^{\infty}f(t)^2\mathrm dt \int \limits_{-\infty}^{\infty}g(t)^2\mathrm dt}}.
